    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "@Haroenv Retrieving it when the middleware starts is only for old versions of search insights now, for this users will have to call `init` if they change their `apiKey`. For modern versions, we retrieve it each time in `sendEvent`, `init` wouldn't work anyway as we use the new signature to force headers.",
